videos.description: Heisman hopeful Saquon Barkley gets the carry and breaks free down the sideline for a 65-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Barkley gets PSU off to roaring start with 65-yard TD

videos.description: Devine Ozigbo pounds through the line for the 1-yard touchdown to give the Cornhuskers the early lead.
videos.headline: Nebraska takes the lead on rushing TD

videos.description: With a 1-yard touchdown run against Nebraska, Saquon Barkley has tied Lydell Mitchell for the most rushing touchdowns in Penn State history with 38.
videos.headline: Barkley ties PSU mark with second TD run of day

videos.description: Trace McSorley beats the Nebraska defense on the option run and goes up the middle for a 9-yard score.
videos.headline: McSorley keeps it for TD

videos.description: Trace McSorley drops back and connects with Mike Gesicki in the corner of the end zone to bolster the Nittany Lions' lead.
videos.headline: McSorley adds passing TD to his stat line

videos.description: Saquon Barkley is officially the all-time leader in rushing touchdowns for Penn State with 39 after this 8-yard run.
videos.headline: Barkley claims PSU record on 3rd TD of day

videos.description: Trace McSorley throws his second touchdown to DeAndre Thompkins putting the Nittany Lions up 32 before half.
videos.headline: Penn State putting on a show with another passing TD

videos.description: Mikale Wilbon gets the call from 24 yards out and motors in for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Nebraska has life following rushing TD

videos.description: Tanner Lee lobs a ball to the end zone and De'Mornay Pierson-El is able to shake off the defender to come down with the touchdown grab.
videos.headline: Cornhuskers take advantage of nice pass for TD

videos.description: Juwan Johnson is able to haul in a one-handed grab and get a foot down while keeping control of the ball for the first down.
videos.headline: Penn State's Johnson with incredible catch

videos.description: Trace McSorley throws his third touchdown pass of the game to Mike Gesicki.
videos.headline: Penn State's offensive clinic continues

videos.description: Tommy Stevens rolls out and connects with Nick Bowers for the 15-yard pitch and catch.
videos.headline: Penn State backup QB tosses TD

videos.description: Tanner Lee throws a perfect ball to the corner of the end zone for Stanley Morgan Jr. who's able to keep his feet in while reeling in the catch with one hand.
videos.headline: Nebraska WR snags 1-handed TD
